            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's a nice school. It's totally academic ,sports day is celebrated here only in leap years.  Children's Day or other special days for students  are not  celebrated here . But on teacher's Day teacher will get biryani ,cold drinks,Momoos and other special dishes. But students don't get anything on children's Day instead of a single eclairs . Some times guardias are abbused by the fees collectors. Even students will not get any\ncraftss,arts,or  any science  projects till class 9. If someone brings a dairy or art book in school it will be taken  by the  prefects. Hence,it is a nice school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
