            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The teachers are good but school is not that good. In summer days its very difficult to sit in the class with 50 students under 2 slow fans. One year later they fixed 1 table fan in our class instead of AC. There are no difference in class before the fan fixed and the class after it. The Fan don't work so well, teacher should provide us that luxury that we deserve.🙄\n\nthe arrogant staff especially the fees collecters are so annoying. they are just disgusting they don't have manners to talk they can't understand that if anyone is not able to pay fees, they should give time, but they don't!\nThey can't understand circumstances, we're going through after the lockdown period!",
